• Knowledge on NFPA 72, IBC & Relevant codes & standards.
• ACAD hands on experience
• Simplex product knowledge will be an advantage
• Understanding the tender documents & specifications.
• Designing of Fire Alarm System IBC, NBC, NFPA 72 etc.
• Must be a quick learner

