JD - 11 :

• *Key Responsibilities:**
- Provide expert level system analysis, design, development, and implementation of applications and databases, including integrating third party products to ensure expected application performance levels are achieved.
- Recommend development options and conduct testing, including functionality, technical limitations, and security aspects.
- Elevate code into the development, test, and production environments on schedule, and provide follow-up production support.
- Offer subject matter expertise in software development methodology and development architecture standards, while mentoring and training staff with less experience.
- Participate in design, code, and test inspections throughout the life cycle, identifying issues and explaining technical considerations at related meetings.
- Understand client business functions and technology needs thoroughly, with a broad and deep understanding of technologies, tools, and applications.
- Interface with cross-functional team members, communicate system issues at the appropriate technical level, and ensure compliance with Information Technology and Information Security policies and procedures.
- Guide integration of complex data flows across distributed services, APIs, and platforms for reliable, secure, and seamless enterprise-level interoperability.
- Drive performance and scalability enhancements by analyzing system behavior, optimizing database architecture, and implementing high-efficiency design patterns.

• *Skills and Attributes for Success:**
- Understanding of Java, Angular, Node JS, POSTMAN, CUCUMBER, AWS, and SQL queries.
- Strong analytical, communication, and interpersonal skills with a team player mindset.
- Ability to stay updated on new technologies, be a trusted advisor to stakeholders, and work with Agile, Confluence, and JIRA.
- Experience in monitoring and refining dashboards, continuous process improvement, and understanding Android, iOS, Nodejs, Typescript, ECS, and Kubernetes.

• *Qualifications Required:**
- Minimum 8 years of experience in application development, system architecture, and database management.
- Bachelor's degree (B.E./) or Master's degree (M.E./) in relevant fields such as Computer Science, Information Technology, Engineering, or a related field.
- Proficiency in Android, iOS, Nodejs, Typescript, ECS, Kubernetes, and understanding of Material Design (Android) and Human Interface Guidelines (iOS).

