JD - 12 :

Principal Activities
• Reviews and clarifies customer requirements and propose a solution based on the Circor product portfolio considering the technical and commercial framework
• Leads expert discussion on plant system configuration and design with the customer and gives advice in terms of technical parameters, system design, material selection, sealing technology, accessories, etc. considering technical and commercial aspects of proposed Circor solutions
• Details the preferred technical solution in cooperation with internal and external interfaces considering commercial aspects
• Elaborates complete technical and commercial quotation. Revises quotation based on feedback/modifications from customer during quote phase and order execution
• Supports field sales team and other sales channels in project negotiations, frame agreements and trade shows
• Supports regional teams with technical expertise for special pumps and applications
• Initiates and conducts trainings in pump and application technology
• Interaction with customers over phone, email and physical visit if necessary to understand application requirements
• Contributes to operational excellence within the organization through continuous improvement of processes, standard and tools.

